CANTLIN
v.
SMYTHE CRAMER CO. 2018-1841 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 17, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motions for admission pro hac vice of Wendy J. Wildung and Peter C. Magnuson. Motions granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission with the Supreme Court's Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
